from\": 2078, \"to\": 2094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sedjati clearly was peaking at the right time, but the Olympic final certainly could be anyone's race, as the entire field has had success at the highest levels: Kenya has dominated the men's 800 in recent Olympics, taking the title each time since 2008 - Wildred Bungei (2008), David Rudisha (2012, 2016) and Emmanuel Korir (2020).\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2260, \"end\": 2265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999996283386972, \"rank\": 3.3786990388588647e-07, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}, {\"begin\": 2377, \"end\": 2390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Rudisha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Rudisha\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Rudisha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Rudisha\"}, {\"begin\": 2408, \"end\": 2422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Korir\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Korir\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Korir\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Korir\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sedjati\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2104}, {\"ngram\": \"the right time\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2142}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic final\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2165}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone's race\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2198}, {\"ngram\": \"the entire field\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2219}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2235}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest levels\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2257}, {\"ngram\": \"recent Olympics\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2311}, {\"ngram\": \"the title\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2329}, {\"ngram\": \"2008 - Wildred Bungei\", \"f